mintRegularTrees(uint256,address).details: Transfer ownership of trees purchased by funders and Update the last tree sold This function is called only by the regularSell contract

params._lastSold: The last tree sold in the regular
params._owner: Owner of a new tree sold in Regular

returns._0: The last tree sold after update

regularPlantTree(string,uint64,uint16).details: This function is called by planter who have planted a new tree The planter enters the information of the new tree Information is stored in The {regularTrees} mapping And finally the tree is waiting for approval

params._countryCode: Code of the country where the tree was planted

requestRegularTree(uint256,address).details: Request to buy a tree with a specific Id already planted and this function transfer ownership to funder This function is called only by the regularSell contract

params._owner: Owner of a new tree sold in Regular
params._treeId: Tree with special Id (The Id must be larger than the last tree sold)

verifyRegularPlant(uint256,bool).details: In this function, the admin approves or rejects the pending trees After calling this function, if the tree is approved the tree information will be transferred to the {treeData}

isTrustedForwarder(address).notice: return if the forwarder is trusted to forward relayed transactions to us. the forwarder is required to verify the sender's signature, and verify the call is not a replay.
